Description: Flask admin application for dmj-vault
 JSON API for managing API keys in the DMJ_VAULT database.
 Provides CRUD operations on API keys and IP whitelists,
 with session-based authentication. Runs under gunicorn
 on 127.0.0.1:9701 by default.
